# 7. GENERATED & EXPORT FILES
# ==============================================
# Applies to: Documentation and Development repos (default excludes)
#
# ⚠️ OPERATIONAL REPOS: ACTION REQUIRED!
# If this is an OPERATIONAL repo that tracks templates/exports,
# COMMENT OUT the patterns below for files you want to version control.
#
# Common operational use cases:
# - Track fillable PDF forms → Comment out: *.pdf
# - Track Word templates → Comment out: *.docx
# - Track Excel templates → Comment out: *.xlsx
# - Track generated reports → Comment out: exports/
# - Track presentation templates → Comment out: *.pptx
#
# Documentation repos: Leave as-is (don't track generated exports)
# Operational repos: Modify as needed (track versioned templates)
# Development repos: Leave as-is (don't track build outputs)

# Content transforms
*.rendered.md
*.export.*

# Exports folder (contains generated reports, outputs)
exports/
generated/

